Publish articles

Usage: mf publish [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Commands:
  run     Publish a file to a target
  update  Update publish record

Options:
      --config <PATH>    
  -v, --verbose...       
  -q, --quiet            
      --format <FORMAT>  [default: text] [possible values: text, json]
      --no-color         
  -h, --help             Print help
  -V, --version          Print version
